came to Mumbai.

00:01:16.985 --> 00:01:21.385
His desire was to be
a musician or a singer.

00:01:21.660 --> 00:01:25.485
In the beginning, Jagjit Singh
used to sing jingles for ads.

00:01:25.760 --> 00:01:28.235
There he met Chitra Singh.

00:01:28.486 --> 00:01:32.273
Though they didn't know at that
time that they would become husband..

00:01:32.523 --> 00:01:34.010
..and wife and get into
a lifelong relationship.

