singing Ghazals..

00:01:57.817 --> 00:02:00.030
..there were already many
big shots in this field.

00:02:00.314 --> 00:02:04.538
Such as Begum Akhtar, Noor Jehan,
Mehndi Hassan and Talat Mehboob.

00:02:04.618 --> 00:02:06.993
But steadily, Jagjit Singh..

00:02:07.230 --> 00:02:10.356
..tried more and more to make
Ghazal singing simpler.

00:02:10.643 --> 00:02:13.772
