singing for films..

00:02:37.876 --> 00:02:41.609
..a new genre of film singing
was presented to the audience.

00:02:41.886 --> 00:02:45.214
Such as the songs for film
'Saath Saath' and 'Arth'.

00:02:45.416 --> 00:02:49.460
"The skirting eyes."

00:02:49.540 --> 00:02:51.526
But Jagjit Singh got
the most popularity..

00:02:51.785 --> 00:02:53.565
