But Jagjit Singh's private
albums made him very popular.

00:03:23.960 --> 00:03:27.500
Jagjit Singh's pairing was
made with many talented poets.

00:03:27.710 --> 00:03:31.591
Such as Javed Akhtar,
Gulzar and Nida Fazli.

00:03:31.780 --> 00:03:36.758
"You make me believe.."

